<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.7.7">
<l>caṉma caṉmāntaraṅ kāttaṭi yārkaḷaik koṇṭupōy</l>
<l>taṉmai peṟuttittaṉ ṟāḷiṇaik kīḻkkoḷḷu mappaṉai</l>
<l>toṉmai pitaṟṟaval lāraip pitaṟṟu mavarkaṇṭīr</l>
<l>naṉmai peṟuttemmai nāḷuyyak koḷkiṉṟa namparē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those, see, who rave about those capable to rave about the ancientness</l>
<l>of the father who, guarding [them] birth after birth leads [his] servants,</l>
<l>making [them] obtain [his] nature [and] takes them under his pair of feet</l>
<l>will be friends who make us obtain goodness [and] take us so that that we escape the days.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
